  "skills": {
    "passive": {
      "name": "We Are Friends",
      "description": "Kupa recovers 10% Max HP per second after not taking damage for 5s. When Kupa is killed, Popol can (Pray) for 3s to bring Kupa back to the battlefield. Cooldown: 30s. Every 3 consecutive attacks from Kupa will enhance Popol's next Basic Attack to deal ( +220% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage). Kupa has 2500 ( +1200% Total Physical Attack) Max HP and inherits 100% of Popol's other attributes and passive equipment effects (excluding Jungling and Roaming equipment effects). Kupa deals an additional damage against Creeps.",
